import React from "react";
import styled from "styled-components";

function BuildPlanMyself(props) {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Header>
        <From>From</From>
        <To>To</To>
      </Header>
      <Details>
        <Date>Date</Date>
        <Days>Number of Days</Days>
      </Details>
      <Family>
        <With>with</With>
        <FamilyName>Family</FamilyName>
      </Family>
      <Plan>
        <PlanHeader>
          <PlanTitle>Daywise Plan</PlanTitle>
          <Day>Day</Day>
          <DayNumber>5</DayNumber>
        </PlanHeader>
        <Images>
          <Image src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/c614b0fd-839a-4044-9b19-1f7504085236?apiKey=57837d822bdf4b509d730a604066e372&" />
          <ImageSpacer />
          <Image src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/5744ff1a-dd40-4377-92c1-b14e209c4fca?apiKey=57837d822bdf4b509d730a604066e372&" />
          <ImageSpacer />
          <Image src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/288c56cb-e4dd-4ba6-b9d6-41eeb142d5a7?apiKey=57837d822bdf4b509d730a604066e372&" />
          <ImageSpacer />
          <Image src="https://cdn.builder.io/api/v1/image/assets/TEMP/8313d432-b66c-4274-a32b-ace55f843797?apiKey=57837d822bdf4b509d730a604066e372&" />
        </Images>
      </Plan>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default BuildPlanMyself;
